Product Description

Set of 30 tattoo stickers

If you are not able to withstand the pain of a real tattoo, you will find it best to add fake to it. The effect of beautiful temporary tattoos is similar to real tattoos. Temporary tattoos are quick and easy to apply by simply applying water to the back of the paper and removing them with alcohol. Our temporary tattoo stickers are unique and long lasting and vibrant just like real tattoos. Moreover, it is non-toxic, easy to remove, durable and will last for many days on your body, suitable for all ages from kids to adults.

Peel and Stick

Easy tattoos without pain. Simply peel off the protective film on the surface, apply it upside down to clean dry skin, wet it thoroughly with water, wait 10-20 seconds to dry, and you can see that the sticker temporarily adheres to body art like a real tattoo. Easy to remove with baby oil or alcohol when changing or removing the tattoo.

Waterproof and long life

Waterproof and non-toxic Tattoos on the back of the ears, neck, arms, upper arms, chest, chest, chest, armpits, hips, thighs, calves, feet, fingers, legs and spine.Do not rub the tattoos with your hands during the summer season. Cute temporary tattoos can be applied anywhere on your body, but also can be applied to non-parrels, mugs, mobiles, furniture, refrigerator tattoos, rock art.

Great for any occasion

Wear our temporary tattoos anytime, anywhere, perfect for daily life, rave party, pool, beach, stag party, music festival, rave night, club night.It can also be applied to several smooth objects such as glass, stationery, paper, plastic, phone case, etc. Great gift for kids and adults.

Easy to use

Fear of pain? Don't worry anymore! Stylish temporary tattoos are easy to use. First wipe the skin clean, then place the design down on your skin, cover with a damp sponge for 20-30 seconds, peel off the backing and you will have the perfect tattoo. Easy to clean with alcohol or baby oil.

Realistic tattoos

Our tattoos are unique, long lasting and vibrant like real tattoos. Moreover, it is non-toxic, easy to remove, durable, and can last for days on the body, so it can be enjoyed by children and adults from all ages.
